{"tid":667113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"椰子又畀人用完即棄","createTime":"2018-05-16T12:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T15:49:36.000Z","uid":136430,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"94def20613908fc69f1f85f6bd4db816f0ba29c2","tid":667113,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c9a422e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】繼艾拿戴斯後，韋斯咸在周三宣佈領隊莫耶斯離隊。<br />\n<br />\n韋斯咸在聲明中指，在去年11月上任、合約僅到季尾的莫耶斯（David Moyes）已完成為球隊護級的使命，跟其助教艾維尼、皮雅斯、麥堅尼都已離隊。聯合主席大衛蘇利雲表示：「我要感謝莫耶斯及其團隊，幫助韋斯咸達成留在英超的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n「莫耶斯來的時候，雙方都希望只專注下半季6個月的事，之後才決定他的前途。以現時的情況及球隊在季尾的表現，我們認為分道揚鑣是正確的決定。我們已經開始物色下任主帥，相信他可以帶領韋斯咸向目標前進。」大衛蘇利雲續說。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的莫天才入主韋斯咸後，成功帶領球隊從降班區回升至第13位，成功護級，但在各項賽事31場只得9勝10和12負，勝率僅29.03%。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933efb1a12b31d7cee68a316f53f7a17217870cc","tid":667113,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3643542121cdddd430074252cbf1075e1d943142","tid":667113,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77bde87df01c6fb5077f3098f64d45e3c4849988","tid":667113,"uid":76753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"大sam去鎚仔<br />\n椰子去拖肥"},{"pid":"0ac915cf8e9135b6f816d50cf3473e0b2c1afa1a","tid":667113,"uid":14436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77bde87df01c6fb5077f3098f64d45e3c4849988","tid":667113,"uid":76753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1